  <h1>Drywall Calculator</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">Calculate how many drywall sheets, joint compound, and tape you need for your room. Accounts for doors, windows, ceilings, and waste.</p>

  <div class="calculator-box">
    <div class="calc-inputs">
      <div class="input-group">
        <label for="roomLength">Room Length (ft)</label>
